s in the same classes. We show in one of the paper appendices that IGR\nJ17315-3221, preliminary classified in the literature as a possible supergiant\nX-ray binary discovered by INTEGRAL, is the product of a data analysis artifact\nand should thus be disregarded for future studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 May 2022 05:34:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-10"}
