e of a release of vaccine-patents\nto reduce the risk of mutation-induced infection revivals but also to\ncoordinate the release of measures following a downwards trend of infection\nnumbers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 May 2022 08:33:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-09"}
