-volatile and reversible tuning of the domain wall dynamics may lead to\napplications to reprogrammable magnetic memories or other spintronic devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 May 2022 11:54:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-06"}
