 van der Waals\nheterostructures and present a photoluminescence study, revealing a significant\nenhancement on the 1L-WS2 optical quality (i.e., higher recombination\nefficiency through neutral excitons) similarly to that obtained on 1L-WS2/hBN\nheterostructures. Our proof-of-concept study shows that phlogopite should be\nregarded as a good and promising candidate for LM-based applications as a\nlow-cost layered nanomaterial.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 May 2022 12:17:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-09"}
