e narrow\nline region.\n  Conclusions. Current VLBI images do not yet show signs of radio outbursts.\nOur observations provide pre-coalescence radio data that are an important\nreference for future comparative studies with the post-merger. In particular,\nfurther resolving the jet will pave the way for probing the dynamical features\nassociated with inspiralling binary black holes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 May 2022 13:37:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-27"}
